    <item>
      <title>Covid Vaccination Clinic</title>
      <link>https://www.ouroakley.uk/events/2026/04/25/covid-vaccination-clinic/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.ouroakley.uk/events/2026/04/25/covid-vaccination-clinic/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Vaccinations are available &lt;strong&gt;from 13 April to 30 June&lt;/strong&gt; for:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;adults aged &lt;strong&gt;75 and over&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;residents in &lt;strong&gt;care homes for older people&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;immunosuppressed&lt;/strong&gt; patients&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This clinic:&lt;/strong&gt; Saturday &lt;strong&gt;25 April&lt;/strong&gt; at Overton Surgery. &lt;strong&gt;Limited capacity&lt;/strong&gt; — book early if you are eligible.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can also &lt;strong&gt;call &lt;a href=&#34;tel:119&#34;&gt;119&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; between &lt;strong&gt;7 April and 29 June&lt;/strong&gt; to book appointments at community pharmacies across the area.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
